{"chapter_number":69,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":78,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"الحاقة","name_complex":"Al-Ĥāqqah","name_simple":"Al-Haqqah","verses_count":52,"pages":[566,568],"meaning":{"text":"The Reality","en":"The Reality","id":"Kenyataan (Hari Kiamat)"},"verses":[[[1,5324,"69:1","الْحَاقَّةُ",["The sure calamity!","Hari Kiamat,"],566,29,57,227,null,null],[2,5325,"69:2","مَا الْحَاقَّةُ",["What is the sure calamity!","apakah hari Kiamat itu?"],566,29,57,227,null,null],[3,5326,"69:3","وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا الْحَاقَّةُ",["And what would make you realize what the sure calamity is!","Dan tahukah kamu apakah hari Kiamat itu?"],566,29,57,227,null,null],[4,5327,"69:4","كَذَّبَتْ ثَمُودُ وَعَادٌ بِالْقَارِعَةِ",["Samood and Ad called the striking calamity a lie.","Kaum Tsamud, dan ‘Ad telah mendustakan hari Kiamat."],566,29,57,227,null,null],[5,5328,"69:5","فَأَمَّا ثَمُودُ فَأُهْلِكُوا بِالطَّاغِيَةِ",["Then as to Samood, they were destroyed by an excessively severe punishment.","Maka adapun kaum Tsamud, mereka telah dibinasakan dengan suara yang sangat keras,"],566,29,57,227,null,null],[6,5329,"69:6","وَأَمَّا عَادٌ فَأُهْلِكُوا بِرِيحٍ صَرْصَرٍ عَاتِيَةٍ",["And as to Ad, they were destroyed by a roaring, violent blast.","sedangkan kaum ‘Ad, mereka telah dibinasakan dengan angin topan yang sangat dingin,"],566,29,57,227,null,null],[7,5330,"69:7","سَخَّرَهَا عَلَيْهِمْ سَبْعَ لَيَالٍ وَثَمَانِيَةَ أَيَّامٍ حُسُومًا فَتَرَى الْقَوْمَ فِيهَا صَرْعَىٰ كَأَنَّهُمْ أَعْجَازُ نَخْلٍ خَاوِيَةٍ",["Which He made to prevail against them for seven nights and eight days unremittingly, so that you might have seen the people therein prostrate as if they were the trunks of hollow palms.","Allah menimpakan angin itu kepada mereka selama tujuh malam delapan hari terus-menerus; maka kamu melihat kaum ‘Ad pada waktu itu mati bergelimpangan seperti batang-batang pohon kurma yang telah kosong (lapuk)."],566,29,57,227,null,null],[8,5331,"69:8","فَهَلْ تَرَىٰ لَهُم مِّن بَاقِيَةٍ",["Do you then see of them one remaining?","Maka adakah kamu melihat seorang pun yang masih tersisa di antara mereka?"],566,29,57,227,null,null],[9,5332,"69:9","وَجَاءَ فِرْعَوْنُ وَمَن قَبْلَهُ وَالْمُؤْتَفِكَاتُ بِالْخَاطِئَةِ",["And Firon and those before him and the overthrown cities continuously committed sins.","Kemudian datang Fir‘aun dan orang-orang yang sebelumnya dan (penduduk) negeri-negeri yang dijungkirbalikkan karena kesalahan yang besar."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[10,5333,"69:10","فَعَصَوْا رَسُولَ رَبِّهِمْ فَأَخَذَهُمْ أَخْذَةً رَّابِيَةً",["And they disobeyed the Messenger of their Lord, so He punished them with a vehement punishment.","Maka mereka mendurhakai utusan Tuhannya, Allah menyiksa mereka dengan siksaan yang sangat keras."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[11,5334,"69:11","إِنَّا لَمَّا طَغَى الْمَاءُ حَمَلْنَاكُمْ فِي الْجَارِيَةِ",["Surely We bore you up in the ship when the water rose high,","Sesungguhnya ketika air naik (sampai ke gunung), Kami membawa (nenek moyang) kamu ke dalam kapal,"],567,29,57,227,null,null],[12,5335,"69:12","لِنَجْعَلَهَا لَكُمْ تَذْكِرَةً وَتَعِيَهَا أُذُنٌ وَاعِيَةٌ",["So that We may make it a reminder to you, and that the retaining ear might retain it.","agar Kami jadikan (peristiwa itu) sebagai peringatan bagi kamu dan agar diperhatikan oleh telinga yang mau mendengar."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[13,5336,"69:13","فَإِذَا نُفِخَ فِي الصُّورِ نَفْخَةٌ وَاحِدَةٌ",["And when the trumpet is blown with a single blast,","Maka apabila sangkakala ditiup sekali tiup,"],567,29,57,227,null,null],[14,5337,"69:14","وَحُمِلَتِ الْأَرْضُ وَالْجِبَالُ فَدُكَّتَا دَكَّةً وَاحِدَةً",["And the earth and the mountains are borne away and crushed with a single crushing.","dan diangkatlah bumi dan gunung-gunung, lalu dibenturkan keduanya sekali benturan."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[15,5338,"69:15","فَيَوْمَئِذٍ وَقَعَتِ الْوَاقِعَةُ",["On that day shall the great event come to pass,","Maka pada hari itu terjadilah hari Kiamat,"],567,29,57,227,null,null],[16,5339,"69:16","وَانشَقَّتِ السَّمَاءُ فَهِيَ يَوْمَئِذٍ وَاهِيَةٌ",["And the heaven shall cleave asunder, so that on that day it shall be frail,","dan terbelahlah langit, karena pada hari itu langit menjadi rapuh."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[17,5340,"69:17","وَالْمَلَكُ عَلَىٰ أَرْجَائِهَا ۚ وَيَحْمِلُ عَرْشَ رَبِّكَ فَوْقَهُمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ ثَمَانِيَةٌ",["And the angels shall be on the sides thereof; and above them eight shall bear on that day your Lord's power.","Dan para malaikat berada di berbagai penjuru langit. Pada hari itu delapan malaikat menjunjung ‘Arsy (singgasana) Tuhanmu di atas (kepala) mereka."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[18,5341,"69:18","يَوْمَئِذٍ تُعْرَضُونَ لَا تَخْفَىٰ مِنكُمْ خَافِيَةٌ",["On that day you shall be exposed to view-- no secret of yours shall remain hidden.","Pada hari itu kamu dihadapkan (kepada Tuhanmu), tidak ada sesuatu pun dari kamu yang tersembunyi (bagi Allah)."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[19,5342,"69:19","فَأَمَّا مَنْ أُوتِيَ كِتَابَهُ بِيَمِينِهِ فَيَقُولُ هَاؤُمُ اقْرَءُوا كِتَابِيَهْ",["Then as for him who is given his book in his right hand, he will say: Lo! read my book:","Adapun orang yang kitabnya diberikan di tangan kanannya, maka dia berkata, “Ambillah, bacalah kitabku (ini).”"],567,29,57,227,null,null],[20,5343,"69:20","إِنِّي ظَنَنتُ أَنِّي مُلَاقٍ حِسَابِيَهْ",["Surely I knew that I shall meet my account.","Sesungguhnya aku yakin, bahwa (suatu saat) aku akan menerima perhitungan terhadap diriku."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[21,5344,"69:21","فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٍ رَّاضِيَةٍ",["So he shall be in a life of pleasure,","Maka orang itu berada dalam kehidupan yang diridhai,"],567,29,57,227,null,null],[22,5345,"69:22","فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٍ",["In a lofty garden,","dalam surga yang tinggi,"],567,29,57,227,null,null],[23,5346,"69:23","قُطُوفُهَا دَانِيَةٌ",["The fruits of which are near at hand:","buah-buahannya dekat,"],567,29,57,227,null,null],[24,5347,"69:24","كُلُوا وَاشْرَبُوا هَنِيئًا بِمَا أَسْلَفْتُمْ فِي الْأَيَّامِ الْخَالِيَةِ",["Eat and drink pleasantly for what you did beforehand in the days gone by.","(kepada mereka dikatakan), “Makan dan minumlah dengan nikmat karena amal yang telah kamu kerjakan pada hari-hari yang telah lalu.”"],567,29,57,227,null,null],[25,5348,"69:25","وَأَمَّا مَنْ أُوتِيَ كِتَابَهُ بِشِمَالِهِ فَيَقُولُ يَا لَيْتَنِي لَمْ أُوتَ كِتَابِيَهْ",["And as for him who is given his book in his left hand he shall say: O would that my book had never been given me:","Dan adapun orang yang kitabnya diberikan di tangan kirinya, maka dia berkata, “Alangkah baiknya jika kitabku (ini) tidak diberikan kepadaku."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[26,5349,"69:26","وَلَمْ أَدْرِ مَا حِسَابِيَهْ",["And I had not known what my account was:","Sehingga aku tidak mengetahui bagaimana perhitunganku."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[27,5350,"69:27","يَا لَيْتَهَا كَانَتِ الْقَاضِيَةَ",["O would that it had made an end (of me):","Wahai, kiranya (kematian) itulah yang menyudahi segala sesuatu."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[28,5351,"69:28","مَا أَغْنَىٰ عَنِّي مَالِيَهْ ۜ",["My wealth has availed me nothing:","Hartaku sama sekali tidak berguna bagiku."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[29,5352,"69:29","هَلَكَ عَنِّي سُلْطَانِيَهْ",["My authority is gone away from me.","Kekuasaanku telah hilang dariku.”"],567,29,57,227,null,null],[30,5353,"69:30","خُذُوهُ فَغُلُّوهُ",["Lay hold on him, then put a chain on him,","(Allah berfirman), “Tangkaplah dia lalu belenggulah tangannya ke lehernya.”"],567,29,57,227,null,null],[31,5354,"69:31","ثُمَّ الْجَحِيمَ صَلُّوهُ",["Then cast him into the burning fire,","Kemudian masukkanlah dia ke dalam api neraka yang menyala-nyala."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[32,5355,"69:32","ثُمَّ فِي سِلْسِلَةٍ ذَرْعُهَا سَبْعُونَ ذِرَاعًا فَاسْلُكُوهُ",["Then thrust him into a chain the length of which is seventy cubits.","Kemudian belitlah dia dengan rantai yang panjangnya tujuh puluh hasta."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[33,5356,"69:33","إِنَّهُ كَانَ لَا يُؤْمِنُ بِاللَّهِ الْعَظِيمِ",["Surely he did not believe in Allah, the Great,","Sesungguhnya dialah orang yang tidak beriman kepada Allah Yang Mahabesar."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[34,5357,"69:34","وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَىٰ طَعَامِ الْمِسْكِينِ",["Nor did he urge the feeding of the poor.","Dan juga dia tidak mendorong (orang lain) untuk memberi makan orang miskin."],567,29,57,227,null,null],[35,5358,"69:35","فَلَيْسَ لَهُ الْيَوْمَ هَاهُنَا حَمِيمٌ",["Therefore he has not here today a true friend,","Maka pada hari ini di sini tidak ada seorang teman pun baginya."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[36,5359,"69:36","وَلَا طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِنْ غِسْلِينٍ",["Nor any food except refuse,","Dan tidak ada makanan (baginya) kecuali dari darah dan nanah."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[37,5360,"69:37","لَّا يَأْكُلُهُ إِلَّا الْخَاطِئُونَ",["Which none but the wrongdoers eat.","Tidak ada yang memakannya kecuali orang-orang yang berdosa."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[38,5361,"69:38","فَلَا أُقْسِمُ بِمَا تُبْصِرُونَ",["But nay! I swear by that which you see,","Maka Aku bersumpah demi apa yang kamu lihat,"],568,29,57,227,null,null],[39,5362,"69:39","وَمَا لَا تُبْصِرُونَ",["And that which you do not see.","dan demi apa yang tidak kamu lihat."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[40,5363,"69:40","إِنَّهُ لَقَوْلُ رَسُولٍ كَرِيمٍ",["Most surely, it is the Word brought by an honored Messenger,","Sesungguhnya ia (Al-Qur'an) itu benar-benar wahyu (yang diturunkan kepada) Rasul yang mulia,"],568,29,57,227,null,null],[41,5364,"69:41","وَمَا هُوَ بِقَوْلِ شَاعِرٍ ۚ قَلِيلًا مَّا تُؤْمِنُونَ",["And it is not the word of a poet; little is it that you believe;","dan ia (Al-Qur'an) bukanlah perkataan seorang penyair. Sedikit sekali kamu beriman kepadanya."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[42,5365,"69:42","وَلَا بِقَوْلِ كَاهِنٍ ۚ قَلِيلًا مَّا تَذَكَّرُونَ",["Nor the word of a soothsayer; little is it that you mind.","Dan bukan pula perkataan tukang tenung. Sedikit sekali kamu mengambil pelajaran darinya."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[43,5366,"69:43","تَنزِيلٌ مِّن رَّبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ",["It is a revelation from the Lord of the worlds.","Ia (Al-Qur'an) adalah wahyu yang diturunkan dari Tuhan seluruh alam."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[44,5367,"69:44","وَلَوْ تَقَوَّلَ عَلَيْنَا بَعْضَ الْأَقَاوِيلِ",["And if he had fabricated against Us some of the sayings,","Dan sekiranya dia (Muhammad) mengada-adakan sebagian perkataan atas (nama) Kami,"],568,29,57,227,null,null],[45,5368,"69:45","لَأَخَذْنَا مِنْهُ بِالْيَمِينِ",["We would certainly have seized him by the right hand,","pasti Kami pegang dia pada tangan kanannya."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[46,5369,"69:46","ثُمَّ لَقَطَعْنَا مِنْهُ الْوَتِينَ",["Then We would certainly have cut off his aorta.","Kemudian Kami potong pembuluh jantungnya."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[47,5370,"69:47","فَمَا مِنكُم مِّنْ أَحَدٍ عَنْهُ حَاجِزِينَ",["And not one of you could have withheld Us from him.","Maka tidak seorang pun dari kamu yang dapat menghalangi (Kami untuk menghukumnya)."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[48,5371,"69:48","وَإِنَّهُ لَتَذْكِرَةٌ لِّلْمُتَّقِينَ",["And most surely it is a reminder for those who guard (against evil).","Dan sungguh, (Al-Qur'an) itu pelajaran bagi orang-orang yang bertakwa."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[49,5372,"69:49","وَإِنَّا لَنَعْلَمُ أَنَّ مِنكُم مُّكَذِّبِينَ",["And most surely We know that some of you are rejecters.","Dan sungguh, Kami mengetahui bahwa di antara kamu ada orang yang mendustakan."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[50,5373,"69:50","وَإِنَّهُ لَحَسْرَةٌ عَلَى الْكَافِرِينَ",["And most surely it is a great grief to the unbelievers.","Dan sungguh, (Al-Qur'an) itu akan menimbulkan penyesalan bagi orang-orang kafir (di akhirat)."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[51,5374,"69:51","وَإِنَّهُ لَحَقُّ الْيَقِينِ",["And most surely it is the true certainty","Dan Sungguh, (Al-Qur'an) itu kebenaran yang meyakinkan."],568,29,57,227,null,null],[52,5375,"69:52","فَسَبِّحْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّكَ الْعَظِيمِ",["Therefore-glorify the name of your Lord, the Great.","Maka bertasbihlah dengan (menyebut) nama Tuhanmu Yang Mahaagung."],568,29,57,227,null,null]],[[[1,11,566,"&#xfbaf;","word","الْحَاقَّةُ",["The Inevitable Reality",""]],[2,11,566,"&#xfbb0;","end","ﮰ",[null,null]]],[[1,11,566,"&#xfbb1;","word","مَا",["What","apakah"]],[2,11,566,"&#xfbd3;","word","الْحَاقَّةُ",["(is) the Inevitable Reality","keadaan yang sebenarnya"]],[3,11,566,"&#xfbd4;","end","ﯔ",[null,null]]],[[1,11,566,"&#xfbd5;","word","وَمَا",["And what","dan apakah"]],[2,11,566,"&#xfbd6;","word","أَدْرَاكَ",["will make you know","kamu mengetahui"]],[3,11,566,"&#xfbd7;","word","مَا",["what","apa"]],[4,11,566,"&#xfbd8;","word","الْحَاقَّةُ",["(is) the Inevitable Reality","keadaan yang sebenarnya"]],[5,11,566,"&#xfbd9;","end","ﯙ",[null,null]]],[[1,11,566,"&#xfbda;","word","كَذَّبَتْ",["Denied","telah mendustakan"]],[2,11,566,"&#xfbdb;","word","ثَمُودُ",["Thamud","kaum Tsamud"]],[3,12,566,"&#xfbdc;","word","وَعَادٌ",["and Aad","dan kaum 'Ad"]],[4,12,566,"&#xfbdd;","word","بِالْقَارِعَةِ",["the Striking Calamity","dengan yang mengejutkan/hari kiamat"]],[5,12,566,"&#xfbde;","end","ﯞ",[null,null]]],[[1,12,566,"&#xfbdf;","word","فَأَمَّا",["So as for","maka adapun"]],[2,12,566,"&#xfbe0;","word","ثَمُودُ",["Thamud","kaum Tsamud"]],[3,12,566,"&#xfbe1;","word","فَأُهْلِكُوا",["they were destroyed","maka mereka dibinasakan"]],[4,12,566,"&#xfbe2;","word","بِالطَّاغِيَةِ",["by the overpowering (blast)","dengan teriakan/kejadian luar biasa"]],[5,12,566,"&#xfbe3;","end","ﯣ",[null,null]]],[[1,12,566,"&#xfbe4;","word","وَأَمَّا",["And as for","dan adapun"]],[2,13,566,"&#xfbe5;","word","عَادٌ",["Aad","kaum 'Ad"]],[3,13,566,"&#xfbe6;","word","فَأُهْلِكُوا",["they were destroyed","maka mereka dibinasakan"]],[4,13,566,"&#xfbe7;","word","بِرِيحٍ",["by a wind","dengan angin"]],[5,13,566,"&#xfbe8;","word","صَرْصَرٍ",["screaming","sangat dingin"]],[6,13,566,"&#xfbe9;","word","عَاتِيَةٍ",["violent","amat kencang"]],[7,13,566,"&#xfbea;","end","ﯪ",[null,null]]],[[1,1